info.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued September 24 at 3:30AM PDT until September 25 at 10:00AM PDT by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM PDT SUNDAY... * WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog. * WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Beaches to Inland Central Coast and Santa Barbara County Central Coast Beaches to Inland Central Coast. * WHEN...Until 10 AM PDT Sunday. * IMPACTS...Very low visibility will create dangerous driving conditions.
info.instruction: If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.
